TO INSTALL

Assuming:
    - you have a jars projects at /var/www/example.com, /var/www/example.net, etc.
    - working jars binary exists at /var/www/example.com/jars etc.
    - your projects require oranfry/jars-refreshd via composer

$ sudo apt install inotify-tools
$ sudo cp jars-refresh@.service.example /etc/systemd/system
$ sudo systemctl daemon-reload
$ sudo systemctl enable jars-refresh@
$ sudo service jars-refresh@example.com start
$ sudo service jars-refresh@example.net start
